fiscal envelope
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a Government limitation on the total amount of money payable to Maori claimants under the Treaty of Waitangi settlements
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: Surfacing again in 1996 as a specific term for Maori refunds
